OL,3,CHugh Grant makes surprise appearance
OL,4,Cat Ashton-in-Makerfield social club
OL,6,FBritish acting legend Hugh Grant has
OL,7,Fmade a surprise visit to a pub in
OL,8,FWigan ahead of tomorrow's landmark
OL,9,FMakerfield by-election.
OL,11,FThe Hollywood star, who's best known
OL,12,Ffor his roles in Notting Hill, Love
OL,13,FActually and Bridget Jones' Diary,
OL,14,Fmade an appearance at Stubshaw Cross
OL,15,FClub in Ashton-in-Makerfield, Wigan on
OL,16,FWednesday 17 June, where Mr Burnham
OL,17,Fwas addressing his supporters.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
