OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781797692
OL,3,CHugh Grant makes surprise appearance
OL,4,Cat Ashton-in-Makerfield social club
OL,6,FThe Greater Manchester Mayor can
OL,7,Freturn to Parliament if he wins the
OL,8,Fseat and has indicated he would put
OL,9,Fhimself forward in an expected
OL,10,Fchallenge to Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,11,Fleadership.
OL,13,FPrevious incumbent Josh Simons stood
OL,14,Fdown last month in order to give Mr
OL,15,FBurnham a potential route back to
OL,16,FWestminster.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
