OL,3,CHugh Grant makes surprise appearance
OL,4,Cat Ashton-in-Makerfield social club
OL,6,FGrant is the latest celebrity to make
OL,7,Fan appearance on the campaign with
OL,8,Fcomedian Steve Coogan supporting Mr
OL,9,FBurnham on the doorstep and TV star
OL,10,FAnt Middleton among those to support
OL,11,Fhis Reform rival Rob Kenyon.
OL,13,FPolling opens at 7am on Thursday 18
OL,14,FJune and closes at 10pm.
OL,16,FThe full list of candidates is
OL,17,Favailable here.
